                "img": "https://arxiv.org/html/2605.06665/2605.06665v1/x1.png",
                "caption": "Figure 1:UniPooloverview.Vanilla MoE allocates a private expert set to each transformer layer, tying expert parameters to depth and preventing cross-layer reuse.UniPoolreplaces layer-private ownership with a single global expert pool while keeping independent per-layer routers. Pool-level balancing aggregates utilization over the shared pool, preventing globally unused experts without forcing every layer to use every expert.",
